    <span><span xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#"><span typeof="v:Breadcrumb"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/" rel="v:url" property="v:title">Code Snippets</a> » <span rel="v:child" typeof="v:Breadcrumb"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/" rel="v:url" property="v:title">CSS</a> » <strong class="breadcrumb_last">A Complete Guide to Flexbox</strong></span></span></span></span>
