        <div class="comment-body group grid-4-5">

          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-author">Robert Fauver</div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#comment-1581248"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> <time datetime="2014-05-15T08:15:23+00:00">May 15, 2014</time></div>
            
          </div>
          
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>The demos are using the new flexbox specs which requires FF 22+</p>

