            <div class="comment-author">Wolf</div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#comment-472802"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> <time datetime="2013-06-27T07:31:03+00:00">June 27, 2013</time></div>
            
          </div>
          
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>Flexbox is now unprefixed in Firefox (22).</p>

            <div class="reply">
              <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/?replytocom=472802#respond" onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "comment-472802", "472802", "respond", "21059" )' aria-label="Reply to Wolf">Reply ↓</a>            </div><!-- .reply -->

