          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>Chris, I couldn’t vertically align some content in print 
media, do you know where I could find more information about this kind 
of support?</p>
<p>My test looks something like this,</p>
<p>CSS:</p>
<pre><code>@page {
    size: US-Letter;
}
article {
    page-break-after: always;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}
article:last-child {
    page-break-after: avoid;
}
</code></pre>
<p>HTML:</p>
<pre><code>&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;article&gt;
        &lt;h1&gt;
            Hello
        &lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;/article&gt;

    &lt;article&gt;
        &lt;h1&gt;
            Hello 2
        &lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;/article&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
</code></pre>

            <div class="reply">
