            <div class="comment-author">Mark F. Simchock</div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#comment-1217009"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> <time datetime="2014-02-28T06:47:14+00:00">February 28, 2014</time></div>
            
