          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>In the first line of the SASS mixin, shouldn’t <code>@mixin flexbox()</code> be just <code>@mixin flexbox</code>?</p>

            <div class="reply">
              <a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/?replytocom=1553572#respond" onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "comment-1553572", "1553572", "respond", "21059" )' aria-label="Reply to Ed">Reply ↓</a>            </div><!-- .reply -->

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->

