          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-author">Chris</div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#comment-1580251"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> <time datetime="2014-04-23T09:14:33+00:00">April 23, 2014</time></div>
            
          </div>
          
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>The .wrapper defined “-webkit-flex-flow: row wrap;” only, add “flex-flow: row wrap;” and it works in IE 11 and Firefox.</p>

