          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>The specification says <code>flex: auto</code> is <code>flex: 1 1 main-size</code>,   to be distinguished from <code>flex: 1 1 auto</code>.  Currently only Firefox  34+  support ‘main-size’.<br>
<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/CSS/flex-basis" rel="nofollow">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/CSS/flex-basis</a></p>

            <div class="reply">
