            <p>There is currently a crippling bug in Firefox that makes 
any non-trivial implementation of flex unfeasible.  Nesting a few flex’d
 containers causes Firefox to become unresponsive.  <a href="https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1082780" rel="nofollow">https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1082780</a></p>

