          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-author">Paul Brady</div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#comment-1597327"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> <time datetime="2015-10-01T17:15:37+00:00">October 1, 2015</time></div>
            
