          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>(Or, correctly…)</p>
<p>To make Flexbox play nicely with iPhone/iPad, add the following metatag…</p>
<p><b>&lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"&gt;</b></p>
<p>Cheers!</p>

