          <div class="comment-author-wrap vcard">
            <div class="comment-author">Wouter</div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#comment-1603732"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> <time datetime="2016-08-26T04:42:29+00:00">August 26, 2016</time></div>
            
