<p>This article has been my “cheat sheet” for flex-box standard.<br>
I have encountered a bug on firefox that does not allow  elements to be flex containers.<br>
It took me AGES to find that out, so I wanna share this with other folks
 that might be going though the pain I have just experienced!</p>
