            <p>You can get some useful insights (and ones very specific 
to your site and users) by installing Google Analytics.  With the 
statistics it gives you, you can see the browser breakdown of the people
 who come to your site.  I think that would let you know how much of a 
need there really is for support for given browser versions.</p>

