            <div class="comment-author">Henry</div> <div class="comment-time"><a href="https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/#comment-1606319"><span class="screen-reader">Permalink to comment</span>#</a> <time datetime="2017-01-24T05:56:13+00:00">January 24, 2017</time></div>
            
          </div>
          
          <div class="comment-content">

            <p>Can I somehow clear align-items for only one of three items?</p>

